'''亡命国度'''（Death of a Nation）是[[美國保守主義|美国保守派]]人士{{en-link|迪內希·杜澤|Dinesh D'Souza}}於2018年拍摄的一部美国政治纪录片<ref>{{Cite web|title=Documentary – Political|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=politicaldoc.htm|accessdate=August 26, 2019|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825151105/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/genres/chart/?id=politicaldoc.htm|archivedate=2019-08-25|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Staff|url=https://apnews.com/4520d07240e34a7c82c5c5c9c0015388|title=‘Gotti’ leads Razzie nominations, Trump up for worst actor|work=apnews.com|publisher=[[美联社|美联社]]|date=January 21, 2019|accessdate=December 26, 2019|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116055751/https://apnews.com/4520d07240e34a7c82c5c5c9c0015388|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在影片中，{{en-link|迪內希·杜澤|Dinesh D'Souza}}将美国第45任总统[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]執政時的政治环境与美國第16任总统[[亚伯拉罕·林肯|亚伯拉罕·林肯]]執政時的政治环境进行比较。影片认为，两个时代的民主党（兩位總統都是共和黨人）都对当时的总统持批判态度，民主党与包括[[纳粹党|纳粹党]]在内的法西斯政权有相似之处。

亡命国度于2018年8月3日在美国上映，票房收入為590万美元。影评人和历史学家批评该片为[[政治宣传|宣传片]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.detroitnews.com/story/entertainment/movies/2018/08/02/review-death-nation-blames-liberals-everything/872484002/|title=Review: 'Death of a Nation' blames liberals for everything|author=Graham|first=Adam|date=August 2, 2018|work=The Detroit News|accessdate=September 5, 2019|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123031648/https://www.detroitnews.com/story/entertainment/movies/2018/08/02/review-death-nation-blames-liberals-everything/872484002/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/ywk59g/dinesh-dsouzas-new-doc-death-of-a-nation-premiered-to-a-hellish-room-of-far-right-stars|title=Dinesh D'Souza’s New Doc Premiered to a Hellish Room of Far-Right Stars|author=Caffier|first=Justin|date=2018-08-07|work=Vice|accessdate=September 5, 2019|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825151100/https://www.vice.com/en_us/article/ywk59g/dinesh-dsouzas-new-doc-death-of-a-nation-premiered-to-a-hellish-room-of-far-right-stars|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2018/07/death-of-a-nation-review-dinesh-dsouza-donald-trump-1201989270/|title=‘Death of a Nation’ Review: Dinesh D’Souza’s Latest Right-Wing Propaganda Compares Donald Trump to Abraham Lincoln|author=Ehrlich|first=David|date=2018-07-30|work=IndieWire|accessdate=September 5, 2019|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212173959/https://www.indiewire.com/2018/07/death-of-a-nation-review-dinesh-dsouza-donald-trump-1201989270/|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及歪曲事实<ref name="herndon">{{Cite news|author=Herndon|first=Astead W.|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/08/17/us/politics/dinesh-dsouza-death-of-a-nation.html|title=A New Film Compares Democrats to Nazis and Trump to Lincoln. At This Screening, It Was a Hit.|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=August 17, 2018|accessdate=August 21, 2018|quote=...the movie has been roasted by actual historians and film critics, who point to the many misrepresentations and falsehoods littered throughout the film.|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202014531/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/08/17/us/politics/dinesh-dsouza-death-of-a-nation.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sarson">{{Cite news|author=Sarson|first=Steven|url=https://historynewsnetwork.org/article/169742|title=Barack Obama: American Historian|work=History News Network|publisher={{link-en|Columbian College of Arts and Sciences}}|date=September 23, 2018|accessdate=January 31, 2019|quote=Numerous journalists and historians such as Kevin M. Kruse and Heather Cox Richardson have exposed D’Souza’s falsehoods...|archive-date=2021-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211107131348/https://historynewsnetwork.org/article/169742}}</ref>。[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]杂志的{{en-link|欧文•格里伯曼|Owen Gleiberman}}表示："{{en-link|迪內希·杜澤|Dinesh D'Souza}}将自由主义和纳粹主义錯誤地混为一谈<ref name="gleiberman">{{Cite magazine|last=Gleiberman|first=Owen|date=July 30, 2018|title=Film Review: Dinesh D’Souza's 'Death of a Nation'|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/reviews/death-of-a-nation-review-dinesh-dsouza-1202890451/|magazine=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝 (雜誌)]]|access-date=July 31, 2018|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212173956/https://variety.com/2018/film/reviews/death-of-a-nation-review-dinesh-dsouza-1202890451/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。" 一些出版物称该片为2018年最差的影片之一<ref name="worst">{{Cite news|author=Staff|url=https://film.avclub.com/the-worst-films-of-2018-1830996584|title=The worst films of 2018|work=[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]|date=December 11, 2018|accessdate=December 12, 2018|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113093235/https://film.avclub.com/the-worst-films-of-2018-1830996584|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]将其列为该网站历史上近12000部影片中排名最差的影片<ref name="metacritic worst">{{Cite news|author=Nordine|first=Michael|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2018/12/worst-movies-2018-metacritic-death-of-a-nation-1202030220/|title=The Worst Movies of 2018, According to Metacritic: 'Death of a Nation' Tops the List|work=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=December 22, 2018|accessdate=December 22, 2018|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201002634/https://www.indiewire.com/2018/12/worst-movies-2018-metacritic-death-of-a-nation-1202030220/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该片還获得了四项[[金酸莓獎|金酸莓獎]]獎項的提名，並最終獲得两项[[金酸莓獎|金酸莓獎]]獎項<ref name="hipes">{{Cite news|author=Hipes|first=Patrick|url=https://deadline.com/2019/01/razzie-awards-nominations-list-donald-trump-gotti-1202538746/|title=Razzie Awards Nominations Are Out: Four Movies 'Lead' In Best Of Worst Race|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=January 21, 2019|accessdate=January 29, 2019|archive-date=2020-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201031224137/https://deadline.com/2019/01/razzie-awards-nominations-list-donald-trump-gotti-1202538746/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

